= The city, unaware

An ordinary late summer in the capital — the crisis grinding, the colonias organizing, nothing on any calendar. **The organizers you have placed in the colonias this season are an investment whose payoff you cannot yet see.** Position them well. The unforeseeable rewards only the prepared.

